    <item>
      <title>墨西哥将法官送上小径首次大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/mexico-sends-judges-on-the-trail-for-first-popular-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥选民首次将在周日开始的竞选活动中选举其法官，这一过程涉及数千名鲜为人知的候选人，这些候选人可能会大大改变该国的权力平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/mexico-sends-judges-on-the-trail-for-first-popular-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
