      <title>哈利王子创立的慈善事业负责人指责他“欺凌”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-30/chairwoman-of-charity-founded-by-harry-accuses-him-of-bullying-and-harassment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏塞克斯公爵（Duke of Sussex）建立的一家慈善机构的负责人指责他试图通过“欺凌”和“骚扰”“驱逐她”。]]></description>
